<title>Foundation &amp; Federal Grants for Hand-Made Classroom Materials &middot; A Teacher's Guide &middot; My Toy Wagon</title>
<meta name="description" content="A guide to federal and foundation grants that fund natural, hand-made classroom materials: NEA Foundation, McCarthey Dressman, Fund for Teachers, Voya Unsung Heroes, plus Title I and ESSER. Award sizes, deadlines, application tips, and sample budgets." />
