  <section class="disclosure">
    <p><strong>One disclosure:</strong> This page describes funding programs as we understand them. We are not affiliated with any of the listed foundations or federal programs, do not administer grants, and cannot guarantee any specific program will fund any specific request. Award amounts, deadlines, and eligibility rules change. Always confirm current details with the granting organization before applying. The "Pairs well with" guidance is based on past educator-customer experience and is not a guarantee that any particular grant will fund a particular bundle.</p>
  </section>

